      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a practical, functional option for those looking for reliable transportation. The exterior shows some signs of age, including minor scratches and a few small dings, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery from regular use. Mechanically, it starts consistently and runs well, though it lacks the refinement of a newer or better-maintained model. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner.",
